{"tid":485464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日丸龜製麵全購「譚仔三哥米線」　計劃進攻珠三角","createTime":"2017-12-01T03:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T09:57:27.000Z","uid":23707,"like":54,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"2c4093637c03996222a761d82ecfac11c17ac762","tid":485464,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"日丸龜製麵全購「譚仔三哥米線」　計劃進攻珠三角<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171201/bkn-20171201104715628-1201_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171201%2Fbkn-20171201104715628-1201_00842_001.html&d=mavyREW5k88UA4jwoGrOxTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=eb17bac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171201/bkn-20171201104715628-1201_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ac1f5b0d17574b809de604bc81719094828ee192","tid":485464,"uid":23707,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:32:09.000Z","msg":"經營「丸龜製麵」的日本Toridoll宣布，已就收購「譚仔三哥米線」100%股權簽訂協議。公告未有提及收購價。<br />\n<br />\nToridoll早於今年5月時收購「譚仔雲南米線」，連同是次收購「譚仔三哥米線」，兩者將續由Toridoll香港子公司共同營運。交易完成後，Toridoll將持有108間「譚仔」分店，包括56間「譚仔三哥米線」及52間「譚仔雲南米線」，在香港雲南米線市佔率擴至約70%。<br />\n<br />\nToridoll指出，有關交易將有效配置公司資源，並實現最大化的協同效應，進一步擴大其米線業務。鑑於珠江三角洲地區有很多人熱愛雲南米線，發展潛力高，公司正計劃將業務拓展至中國，以華南為首個目標市場。<br />\n<br />\n此外，公司考慮將業務擴展至東南亞和美國等許多中國人聚集的地區。"},{"pid":"c747aa094449228185af1cc5fac4c78fe9f48bc5","tid":485464,"uid":10949,"like":133,"dislike":2,"score":131,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:32:44.000Z","msg":"三哥嘅理想敵唔過銀彈攻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ee66445eb530a7243eba3c4228cabf419be657","tid":485464,"uid":23707,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三哥嘅理想敵唔過銀彈攻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢既理想係咩"},{"pid":"19599939d84af3be03e1f07052413f438ff661c8","tid":485464,"uid":10949,"like":195,"dislike":1,